        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 2. Compound eyes of Bryothinusa spp.A – B. algarum Sawada, 1971; B – B. minuta (Sawada, 1955); C – B. tsutsuii (Sawada, 1955); D – B. koreana Ahn & Jeon, 2004; E – B. yoshigoui sp. nov.; F – B. japonica Liu, Ono & Maruyama, 2020; G – B. sakishimana Sawada, 1991; H – B. constricta sp. nov.; I – B. hokkaidensis sp. nov.; J – B. fulvipennis sp. nov.; K – B. itsuroi sp. nov.; L – B. aikoae sp. nov.; M – B. okinawana sp. nov.; N – B. nigra sp. nov.; O – B. nakanei (Sawada, 1955); P – B. moriguchii sp. nov.; Q – B. gangjinensis Ahn & Jeon, 2004. Scale bars: 0.05 mm." ;
